## 6. Where to look next

If you are starting from scratch:

1. Read `hybrid/test/handoff_roundtrip.S` first - it is the simplest
   round-trip fixture and demonstrates the three-phase template.
2. Then `tests/hybrid/roundtrip_e2e.sh` to see how a fixture is driven.
3. Then `src/simulator.hpp` (`apply_resume_from_qemu`,
   `enable_hybrid_handoff`, the run loop) to see how the simulator
   reacts to the trigger.
4. `hybrid_plan.md` has the longer-form rationale and phase plan that
   this document distills.
